issue_body:
@Ape , using this project we are able to connect to the TV(model UE55LS003) successfully.
With the key combination KEY_SOURCE and KEY_HDMI4 we are able to switch to the HDMI4. now we are trying to put it back to TV source, but it is not happening. We tried KEY_SOURCE and KEY_TV, then we tried KEY_SOURCE and KEY_DTV. But nothing seems to be working. Are we missing something or is it issue with the KEY value.
Thanks for your help.

Code references example "Listen for notifications at IPv4 & IPv6 interfaces" as:
+++
 if reqPDU.isSameTypeWith(pMod.TrapPDU()):
            if msgVer == api.protoVersion1:
                
